OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome patchy low cloud in places
OL,6,Fat first, but widespread sunshine will
OL,7,Fdevelop through the morning to give a
OL,8,Fgenerally fine day. Cloud may linger
OL,9,Ftowards the Lincolnshire coast, where
OL,10,Fit will feel cooler with an onshore
OL,11,Fbreeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FPatchy low cloud will return
OL,14,Finto the evening, with areas of mist
OL,15,Fand fog developing later in the night.
OL,16,FChilly, with an isolated frost
OL,17,Fpossible as winds fall light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
