OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FEarly low cloud, mist and
OL,6,Ffog soon clearing to give another fine
OL,7,Fand dry day with long sunny spells and
OL,8,Flight winds. Mild inland, but cooler
OL,9,Ftowards the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,12,Ffine and warm during this period with
OL,13,Fplenty of sunny spells and light
OL,14,Fwinds. Chilly at times overnight with
OL,15,Fsome patchy overnight fog possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
